The 95-year-old monarch is said to be "terrified" disaster could strike- threatening the line of succession and has told Prince William to stop flying in helicopters with his family. A source close to the Queen claimed: "It keeps the Queen awake at night and she is understandably very worried."It comes as royal expert Jonathan Sacerdoti claims Prince Charles plans to "slim down" the monarchy when he takes the throne. FOLLOW BELOW FOR UPDATES...